{
  "stem": "26790.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I wanted to tell you the details of how this happen, how this happen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was condition.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When it reminds me, it's making me sick how conditions, what was in that time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A miracle happen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A miracle happen, when I become-- when I become apprentice by a furrier, a fur coat-- fur coat maker, a furrier, making fur coats.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A miracle happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I will-- please, let me--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I [INAUDIBLE] repeat.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't like to repeat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Let me please, let go this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this is special.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because this is a very important matter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is lesson for you, young people, to know how we were living at that time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And those conditions we were living, and how it-- how it was-- how hardship it was to a young boy or young girl to be become apprentice, an apprentice by a tailor, or a shoemaker, or a carpenter, or a painter, how hard it was.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because you have-- first of all, you have to-- if you want to become apprentice by a tailor, or a shoemaker, a carpenter, an electrician, you have to pay the boss 300 zlotys to become apprentice.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In two years you have to work for nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the first six months-- in the first six month, apprentices have to do everything that in the house, cleaning, shopping, and doing, and clean up the baby and everything, everything.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Six months he doesn't do nothing at work, just looking for the house, that's all.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's what condition.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's what I wanted, please let me stick when I will have a chance to speak, I will explain to you.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this will be a good lesson for you, a good lesson for you, how we were living.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
